      About this Journal

      Limnology and Oceanography: Methods publishes articles describing newly developed laboratory and field methods in all areas of the aquatic sciences. The journal is not intended as a vehicle for publishing original research that only incidentally employs new methods, and manuscripts that are not focused on methods will not be accepted.
